'''Conad''' (''{{lang|it|Consorzio Nazionale Dettaglianti}}'') is an Italian retail store brand which operates one of the largest [[supermarket]] chains in [[Italy]].<ref>[http://www.board.com/us/case-studies-12/2013-01-10-17-44-07/item/713-conad-del-tirreno Board International] - Caste Study: CONAD del Tirreno</ref> Created in 1962, Conad is a [[cooperative]] system of [[entrepreneur]]s, dealing in large-scale distribution. It is structured on three levels: entrepreneur members (owners of retail outlets), cooperatives (large shopping and distribution centers), and the national consortium (a service and market-oriented body for member companies)<ref>[http://www.conad.it/conad/home/global/chi-siamo/consorzio-nazionale-dettaglianti/storia.html CONAD] - Our History (Italian).</ref>
